{"tid":982941,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"疑不滿淡友圍插 低置仔月租/ihavetoldyou拎關刀宣戰","createTime":"2019-01-15T13:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T14:32:08.000Z","uid":163207,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dacdfe3641d67914870aecbb69e3476ddf862409","tid":982941,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"昨晚10時許，一名身穿背心黑褲的長髮男子，帶同逾2米長、用布包着刀刃的懷疑關刀，在連燈財經台對開揮舞，又自拍片段上載至某色情網站，指「全部烏合之眾，等緊你呀，講就如何如何長江黃河，落嚟呀，我買股票嘅嘢你要管！樓爆未呀?! 出嚟battle呀! 報警係最好嘅，你最好就報警，一係就我去報警」，當中夾雜大量粗口，有網民發現片段擔心報admin。<br />\n<br />\n連仔接報後派搜索犬到場，其後在高爆區對面的精液味低置區搜索，最終在一回覆內發現該名32歲男子，調查後案件列誤會，事件中沒有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n據網民表示，該男早前在財經台出post時，疑只重注買牛，未有及時止蝕，其後又稱早已對沖，事件被上載連燈後他出言反擊，被網民「恥笑」，繼而引發今次事件。亦有網民表示，時不時看見他，「真係一年四季都鳩叫，之前都見過佢揸關刀，以為佢玩Cosplay。」"},{"pid":"f63083a4969fc6594f7b95743c60b09140a69494","tid":982941,"uid":163207,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190114/large/1547413284_c2d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190114%2Flarge%2F1547413284_c2d9.jpg&h=61259815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關刀示意圖"},{"pid":"57661343ee170b291287304474463a0cbcc7cff7","tid":982941,"uid":163207,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:38:33.000Z","msg":"負評快到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180c5735745e036a81eabae9f53fac7befbc7718","tid":982941,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e84b78d841245d13c140d0f870d85f3df51c72a","tid":982941,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"180c5735745e036a81eabae9f53fac7befbc7718","tid":982941,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"唔敢入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}